    ;; ── LT8618SX MIPI DSI → HDMI 2.0 Transmitter ───────────────────────────
    ;; QFN-56, 8×8mm, 0.5mm pitch
    ;; Input: MIPI DSI 4-lane from QRB2210 via switch
    ;; Output: HDMI 2.0 (4K@30fps) via micro-HDMI Type D receptacle
    ;; I2C control: address 0x75 (default) from QRB2210 or STM32U585
    ;; EDID: internal, reads from HDMI sink via DDC channel
    ;; HDCP: supported (optional — can disable in firmware)
